TRY THIS BUSINESS TO CHANGE YOUR LIFE

Do I Need To Invite People In This Business?

Many people who has experience with a traditional sales and business opportunity are asking...

"Do I Need To Invite People In This Business?"

"Kaylangan ko bang mag-invite ng mga tao?"

The answer is NO!

Hindi mo kaylangang mag-invite or kumausap ng mga tao.

Unity Network is not MLM or Network Marketing where you need to invite and talk to people. You also don't have to present or sell anything.

How Do YOU Make Money In This Business?

Unity Network business model is called affiliate marketing. And to make money with this business model (affiliate marketing), your only goal is to make people click your affiliate link.

That affiliate link is unique and coded to you. This is how we identify who refers a new customer. This is how we know who gets the commission.

When people clicks your link, the system and the marketing will immediately take over.

Our system will do all the selling, the follow up and the upselling process for you. When they make a purchase, that is where you earn a commission.

Your commission will depends on what product(s) your referral bought and what membership level you are in.

What's The Difference Of Inviting and Promoting?

Inviting is a one to one process. Ito yung kakausap ka ng mga KKK mo. Kakilala, Kamaganak, Kaibigan para alukan ng products at business mo.

This approach is usually teach in Network Marleting and MLM types of business model. We do NOT do this and we do NOT recommend this approaches because you can not scale your business with it.

Promoting however is one to many process. You are marketing to many people. Some example of promotions that you can do is by publishing content on the internet, placing ads on facebook or youtube, sending emails to a subscriber list, hosting live video broadcast like FB live and more.

This is what we teach our students because it is more efficient and it's scalable. You can reach more people fast using this approach and you can grow your business much quicker.

Again your goal when you promote is not to sell the products of Unity Network. Your goal is to make people click your affiliate link, then the system will do the rest.

Luxury Semi-D @ Saujana Duta Seremban 2 S2 Top Hill Seremban 2  

Selling Price: 1.59 million (nego)    

Justin 016-263 8268

-2 2/1 Storey Semi-D
-Land Area: 40x80
-Build-up: 4,038 sq.ft 
-5 bedrooms + 6 bathrooms + 2 big halls
-Freehold 
-Non-bumi
-Good location – Top Hill

Being the only development that occupies the hilltop land, Saujana Duta at Seremban 2 is an exclusive low density enclave, comprising only 199 units of luxurious semi-detached homes and bungalows with a private clubhouse. Located 400 feet above sea level on an elevated nature platform, this development offers cool and refreshing air everyday, as well as stunning views of the surrounding greenery and of the city skyline.
The 38-acre Saujana Duta was developed in two phases. The first phase comprises 116 units of semi-detached homes and eight units of bungalows. Meanwhile, the 2nd phase of Saujana Duta features 75 units of signature bungalows. The semi-detached homes are available in two different design and layout options, with selling price from RM1.77 million. Meanwhile, the selling price for the two-storey bungalow starts from RM2.52 million. To date, 70% of the non-Bumi units have been taken up.
The Hilltop Recreational Villa is the development’s very own signature clubhouse, available exclusively for the residents. It is an imposing architectural masterpiece that sits on the edge of the hill. The gymnasium in the clubhouse enjoys ample natural light due to the full length glass walls, and the infinity lap is strategically placed to allow swimmers to enjoy the breathtaking view of the tranquil environment. Other facilities in the clubhouse include function rooms, lookout points and lounge areas for gathering or private parties.
The development is further enhanced by a multi-tiered security system. The single entry and exit point is safeguarded by a security checkpoint with CCTV surveillance. The perimeter fencing also comes with CCTV and round-the-clock security patrol. In addition, homes are equipped with individual fencing, CCTV, home alarm system and panic button.
Within the enclave, much has been done by IJM Land to provide a wholesome and healthy living experience for the whole family. For instance, the Saujana Duta enclave is encircled by a signature 1.7 km cycling and jogging track that connects the three themed gardens that act as meeting points for the residents.
The three themed gardens consist of:
•  Sunrise Green (facing east): A small pocket park that lets residents rest on the benches while watching the sun rise from the horizon
•  Sunset Green: One can enjoy the best view of a sunset
•  Wellness Green: Numerous reflexology facilities are available for the residents
On top of these, Saujana Duta is situated right beside a 30-acre Hill Park @ S2 Heights, which offers a panoramic sweeping view of Seremban 2 and its surrounding landscapes.
Saujana Duta is designed to be one of the most modern, innovative and future-ready homes, and it’s easy to see why. A host of technologically-advanced and environmentally-conscious features can be found in these homes, and they include home automation system, which allows the controlling of selected appliances with a smart phone or a tablet; rainwater harvesting system, which saves water by collecting and reusing rainwater and solar water heating system, which saves energy by utilising solar power. The homes are also ready with high-speed fibre Internet to welcome their new inhabitants.
The architectural design of the Phase 2 bungalows fosters a sense of elegance and privacy. Each bungalow sits on plots measuring 6,400 sq ft to 13,000 sq ft and offers built-up areas of between 5,000 sq ft to 6,500 sq ft. The layout has been sensitively crafted to offer spacious, airy, calm and relaxed environment, as well as to optimise its magnificent surroundings. In addition, the layout offers a perfect integration between the indoor and outdoor.
Every bungalow comes with a signature 10-foot tall main entrance door, large and abundant glass panels, premium finishes (800mm x 800mm porcelain tiles, engineered wood flooring for first floor, stainless steel water tank with water pump), lavish bathroom fittings (granite vanity top & glass shower compartments), high ceiling and green home features (rain water harvesting, solar panel & tinted glass), perfectly harmonised to convey a sense of luxury and beauty.

Analysis
As one of the pioneers in the property industry, IJM Land has developed many prominent developments to date. To name a few, they are Granview, Debunga Residensi, Pantai Sentral Park, Seri Binjai and Senjayu.
Saujana Duta is strategically located within minutes' drive away from several amenities and among them are Mydin Hypermarket, Tesco Extra, Columbia Asia Hospital, KPJ Seremban Hospital, Palm Mall, Rasah Kemayan Golf and Country Club, SMK Kepayang, SRK Wawasan, SMK Taman Bukit Kepayang and Alpha Technology College.
In terms of accessibility, the Seremban KTM Station is located merely 20 minutes drive away from this residence. Meanwhile, the North - South Highway further connects this area to other neighbourhoods.
IJM Land envisions Saujana Duta to be more than just a residential enclave that sets the benchmark for luxury living in Seremban. One of the main ideas behind Saujana Duta is to build an enclave that is defined by its community and people. This is why, every element of Saujana Duta, from the jogging and cycling track to the themed gardens and the Hilltop Recreational Villa, is a result of the vision of building a close-knit community.
